         <PROCEDURE>
            <PT_OPEN/>
            <ACCELERATED_PROC>
               <P>The Cardiff and Vale University Health Board have secured end of year money to replace the WEDINOS laboratory equipment that is no longer fit for purpose and has obsolete replacement parts. The funding will replace the kit which in turn will allow the current procedures for WEDINOS to continue. As there is no national equipment framework currently available to utilise, the Health Board needs to go out to market via a compliant process and given the time restrictions to spend the money by 31st March, has agreed that the Accelerated Open Procedure best fits the requirement to appropriately procure and receive the equipment in the timeframe available.</P>
            </ACCELERATED_PROC>
